openvswitch: Open vSwitch (multilayer software network switch)
openvswitch:
openvswitch: Open vSwitch is a multilayer software switch licensed under the open
openvswitch: source Apache 2 license.  Our goal is to implement a production
openvswitch: quality switch platform that supports standard management interfaces
openvswitch: and opens the forwarding functions to programmatic extension and
openvswitch: control.
openvswitch:
openvswitch: Open vSwitch is well suited to function as a virtual switch in VM
openvswitch: environments.  Open vSwitch supports multiple Linux-based
openvswitch: virtualization technologies including KVM, and VirtualBox.
